If I want to merge master branch code in branch xyz then code will be like :
git branch 
branch xyz
*master
git merge branchxyz
git conflict occurs when same name file made by you in different branch then conflict occurs
If conflict occurs while merging master branch file1 to branch xyz file1 then code will be like:
vi file1
